Titolo: Resident Evil Village

Anno: 2021

Descrizione: Resident Evil Village is a 2021 survival horror game developed and published by Capcom. It is the sequel to Resident Evil 7: Biohazard (2017). Players control Ethan Winters, who is searching for his kidnapped daughter after a fateful encounter with Chris Redfield, and finds himself in a village filled with mutant creatures. Village maintains the Resident Evil series' survival horror elements, but uses more action-oriented gameplay.
Resident Evil Village was announced at the PlayStation 5 reveal event in June 2020 and was released on May 7, 2021, for Windows, PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Stadia, Xbox One, and Xbox Series X/S. It received generally favorable reviews, with praise for its gameplay, setting, and variety, although it received criticism for its puzzles, boss fights and performance problems on the Windows version, and the increased focus on action divided opinion. Resident Evil Village won multiple year-end accolades, including Game of the Year at the Golden Joystick Awards.

Genere: Non specificato


Valutazione: 82
